---
title: Chipotle Beef and Quinoa Bowl with Pico de Gallo and Chipotle Crema
description: Seasoned with a touch of chipotle powder, this beef bowl packs more than a heat punch. A bed of quinoa tossed with spinach gets topped with roasted sweet potatoes while ground beef gets a flavour boost from our Southwest Spice Blend. The cooling pico de gallo and chipotle crema complements perfectly.
